{"tid":1726924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[摺被軍對策]務必要準備定Banner","createTime":"2019-11-16T09:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T09:44:26.000Z","uid":97821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"49f884fcf8ac5b28e44257e049ab76680bdeb044","tid":1726924,"uid":97821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:43:46.000Z","msg":"Banner要中英文寫 <br />\n追究8964解放軍屠城責任，<br />\n共匪竊國，天滅中共等等。<br />\n可以掛係屋外牆，唔一定要用人手拉，避免同黑警曱同廢藍屍直接衝突。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n類似嘅banner要時刻都要準備好， 人地一出手就要快速掛好，務求紅媒直播拍片影相都要有banner入鏡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b593d5e64093f0598290812850b69346e5067eee","tid":1726924,"uid":222269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:44:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}